root: ^[Rowan] You should be careful! I saw you climbing to the roof over there. Your mom would agree with what I have to say.
^[Addison] I saw that there’s a locked gate up there. Is there a key to unlock it?
^[Rowan] Why do you need to unlock that gate?
^[Addison] Oh, I saw something behind the gate and I wanted to see it.
^[Rowan] Hm… I can’t remember who last opened the gate or who even has the key.
^[Addison] Is there anything I can do to break the gate?
^[Rowan] Addison! Good grief, don’t you become a vandalizer now. Let me— OH I remember! Larry last had the key because he needed to store his fishing gear.
